Turteltaub produced the CBS television series, Jericho, and also directed the first three episodes, \"Pilot\", \"Fallout\", and \"Four Horsemen\".", "New York City, New York, USA", 3.153, "/borF48XTUkOCKE3ryh3BFxe4Unr.jpg"),
